data.text: @adsausage Ah 1947. Newer versions have gone arty-farty. The latest one's an easier read than the one before.
@keith_johnson Home was definitely first. I have back issues from 1947! Both great supplements though.
@adsausage @shelbygrad @latimes Gosh, don't recall all the various versions of those Sunday LATimes magazines. Perhaps Home was the first version.
